n rural china and is c urrently leading a project to deliver basic health interventions to chinese schoolchildren in underprivileged areas she has published several papers in food policy china economics review and agricultural economics publications the 5 most recent are displayed more publications college is a rich han urban male club research notes from a census survey of four tier one colleges in china xiaobing wang chengfang liu linxiu zhang renfu luo scott rozelle china quarterly 2011 pdf+ alarmingly high anemia prevalence in western china renfu luo xiaobing wang chengfang liu linxiu zhang yaojiang shi grant miller scott rozelle elaine yu reynaldo martorell southeast asian journal of tropical medicine and public health vol 42 5 2011 pdf+ college education and the poor in china documenting the hurdles to educational attainment and college matriculation xiaobing wang chengfang liu linxiu zhang renfu luo thomas glauben yaojiang shi scott rozelle brian sharbono asia pacific education review 2011 pdf+ what is keeping the poor out of college enrollment rates educational barriers and college matriculation in china xiaobing wang chengfang liu linxiu zhang renfu luo thomas glauben yaojiang shi scott rozelle brian sharbono china agricultural economic review 2011 pdf+ early commitment on financial aid and college decision making of poor students evidence from randomized evaluation in rural china chengfang liu linxiu zhang renfu luo scott rozelle brian sharbono jennifer adams yaojiang shi ai yue hongbin li xiaobing wang thomas glauben economics of education review 2011 pdf+ stanford university all rights reserved 650 723 2300 terms of use copyright complaints rss+ rss xml feeds
